reviews.text: Nice hotel to stay for business if you have a office nearby. Nearer to mrt and  market place. Good and many options for lunch and dining options. Bit expensive compared to other hotels. Not much option for breakfast nor lunch or dinner. Okay bar on the top floor but nothing to write home about!
Very helpful and friendly staff. They even helped me recover a lost item. Rooftop bar is great.

Was a pleasure to stay there. The location is good, not the heart of Hong Kong but good location. The room is clean and the staff is very kind and welcoming. It's a modern hotel with unique design and they speak english well. I highly recommand and we will go there again for sure.

Stayed here twice now and have had a great experience both times.  Rooms are nice and quirky with comfortable beds.  There's plenty of great places to eat and drink in nearby and the nearby toy market is ideal for those presents before you go home!
Very nice hotel close to the subway. Nice pool on the rooftop.

reviews.text: Nice hotel to stay for business if you have a office nearby. Nearer to mrt and  market place. Good and many options for lunch and dining options. Bit expensive compared to other hotels. Not much option for breakfast nor lunch or dinner. Okay bar on the top floor but nothing to write home about!
港岛英迪格酒店为香港最多元化的历史邻里之一的湾仔带来一股新的动力。酒店崭新和时尚的设计刻意唤起其丰富的邻里文化环境。通过独特设计和艺术作品，每间客房也会捕捉到邻里历史和文化。在屋顶上，你会发现充满现代气息的SkyBar和扣人心弦的无边玻璃底游泳池。围绕酒店都是各其特色的商店，市场，餐馆和酒吧。你亦可漫步各景点，深深体会充满丰富历史的湾仔。我们的团队将很乐意与您分享他们的邻里故事。
Very helpful and friendly staff. They even helped me recover a lost item. Rooftop bar is great.
